# Markdown & MDX are hand-authored to conventions Prettier cannot honor — see
# docs/markdown-style.md. With no option to disable, Prettier would:
#   - rewrite `*emphasis*` to `_emphasis_` (the guide requires `*`)
#   - reflow prose and collapse the authored line breaks that frontmatter
#     `description` fields render verbatim
#   - mangle escaped heading anchors (\{#id})
# So keep all Markdown out of Prettier and format it by hand.
*.md
*.mdx
